 - Pala farki: Aider hizlidir; Pala o hizin ustune audit ve court bindirir.
 
+## Market Radar Core 10
+
+Dashboard artik bu daha genis pazar radarini da gosterir. Bu tablo "bunu kopyala" listesi degildir; Pala'nin hangi sinyali hangi kontrol sinirina cevirdigini yazar.
+
+| Reference | Signal | Pala control answer |
+| --- | --- | --- |
+| OpenAI Codex CLI | Lokal terminal coding agent ve approval/SDK yuzeyi | Codex tekrar yazilmaz; Pala task scope, evidence ve court ile kontrol eder |
+| OpenHands | SDK/API/React GUI ayrimi olan agent platformu | Pala core/daemon/dashboard ayrimini korur, ama truth DB + ledger + court kalir |
+| Cline | IDE/CLI/SDK agent runtime | Pala runtime satmaz; runtime etrafinda governance board olur |
+| Goose | Rust local-first desktop + CLI + API | Rust/Tauri wrapper ileride degerlendirilebilir; once kontrol modeli kanitlanir |
+| Continue | Repo-native checks ve CI gate disiplini | Pala checks local court ve evidence ledger ile genisletilir |
+| PR-Agent | GitHub Action/App/local CLI PR reviewer modeli | Pala PR yorumundan daha genis diff manifest, source-card ve release gate ister |
+| GitHub Agent HQ | Multi-agent mission control | Pala ayni yonu local-first, owner-controlled ve evidence-backed olarak hedefler |
+| Port AI Control Center | AI-created PR dashboard ve agent attribution | Pala bunu local ledger + GitHub read/write ayrimi ile uygular |
+| Agent Friendly Code | Repo/site agent-readiness scorecard | Pala score'u action queue, standards ve court blocker'a cevirir |
+| Microsoft Agent Governance Toolkit | Policy, identity, sandboxing ve SRE for agents | Pala Court/Evidence katmaninin ciddi bir governance kategorisi oldugunu dogrular |
+
+## PM / Shipping Doctrine Candidate
+
+`phuryn/pm-skills` Pala icin runtime ya da core dependency degildir. Source-carded PM/shipping doctrine adayi olarak tutulur.
+
+- En faydali bolum: `pm-ai-shipping`
+- Pala mapping:
+  - vibe-coded app shipping packet
+  - intended-vs-implemented audit
+  - test coverage map
+  - architecture / permission / secrets documentation discipline
+- Boundary:
+  - kod import yok
+  - command/plugin install yok
+  - once source-card, license, risk, allowed layer ve local proof
+
 ## Current Local Stack
 
 - Node 24 built-in `node:sqlite` -> local DB
